{"tid":1017361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海洋公園搞鬼屋設計比賽","createTime":"2019-02-11T11:35:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T09:30:53.000Z","uid":34409,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a9bc7cae4e0dbd9e98a2aa06eb836dee0fb83c72","tid":1017361,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T11:35:56.000Z","msg":"$5000可以公然招收一堆鬼屋idea <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6nqxvg89\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6nqxvg89&h=e5417446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n獎項：<br />\n評審將選出最佳鬼屋設計方案為優勝者，勝出隊伍可獲得以下獎品：<br />\n<br />\n港幣$5,000元獎學金<br />\n每位成員可獲「海洋公園哈囉喂全日祭2019」優越門票2張<br />\n<br />\n勝出隊伍之鬼屋設計有機會於「海洋公園哈囉喂全日祭2019」採用及參與海洋公園的專業設計團隊的設計工作"},{"pid":"7150ff45dfe48d638ddb93c8b2e7249ca5c4b5dd","tid":1017361,"uid":63864,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T11:37:45.000Z","msg":"好多大公司都係咁樣扼idea"},{"pid":"d0c255ba64f5c7ddcfcd03f38f0030b2b29cb1b2","tid":1017361,"uid":29093,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T11:46:39.000Z","msg":"5000 蚊 分分鐘買哂 top 10 既idea <br />\n表面就得 top 1 有獎 <br />\n但top 2 至 10 就免費抄idea <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e8ad5b125004753d4c0b893c5a00ea360cb76f","tid":1017361,"uid":65429,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T11:52:03.000Z","msg":"其實鬼屋呢啲,愈有本土味生活化愈恐怖<br />\n迪士尼果d完全唔恐怖,因為好撚離地<br />\n公屋/升降機/醫院/學校/街市/中式靈堂呢啲一定最嚇到香港人/大陸人/亞洲人"},{"pid":"df9440fc38ca38baeb79531b37ebe9f1472a7d1f","tid":1017361,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T11:56:34.000Z","msg":"蝗蝻廢老混雜公屋"},{"pid":"be8571d0213026d7bc9facbe0a97953d50f746fd","tid":1017361,"uid":232754,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T11:56:49.000Z","msg":"間鬼屋入左去好似羅湖城咁，會有鬼（大陸人）搶嘢、用針